<span id="freeTextContainer3878581701585084235">Written in a light and humorous tone, <i>You Are Not So Smart</i> is a nice introduction to several different areas of psychology. Never diving too deep into the science, each chapter gives examples and case studies into why we behave and think the way we do. If you are new to psychology, or looking for a light read on the subject, this is a good place to start.</span>

          </span>
